Files should be located in default hooks directory /etc/pacman.d/hooks/ or in directory specified in /etc/pacman.conf

Modify access rights to files:

sudo chmod a+rx,u+w tomcat.sh
sudo chmod a+r,u+w tomcat.hook

To look like this: ls -lA
-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 169 Sep  7 16:44 tomcat.hook
-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root 362 Sep  7 16:22 tomcat.sh*
